Name: Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the execution of SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-AE Assign Reviewers following SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in cases where at least one reviewer agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time for SW-AE Assign Reviewers when followed by Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Minimum time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer No Response
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response'

Name: Total time until SW-AE Assign Reviewers is performed after SW-Reviewer Selection is now due
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and the next occurrence of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the execution of SW-AE Assign Reviewers compared to the average time it takes SW-Reviewer Declined after SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in variants that include multiple reviewer assignment attempts versus variants with a single assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-AE Assign Reviewers and the end of the case

Name: Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in cases that eventually result in SW-EIC Major Revision
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Total time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Unavailable across all process variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Unavailable'

Name: Minimum cycle time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers when immediately followed by SW-Reviewer Agreed without any reminder activities
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'
